OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,FThe remains of a further 22 infants
OL,7,Fhave been found at the site of a
OL,8,Fformer mother and baby home in Co
OL,9,FGalway.
OL,11,FThe search, which began in July last
OL,12,Fyear, has so far discovered the
OL,13,Fremains of 99 infants at the site.
OL,15,FThe most recently found remains were
OL,16,Flocated in the search period from June
OL,17,F1 to July 15, in an area that had been
OL,18,Fcovered with gravel and used for
OL,19,Fvehicle access, with no surface
OL,20,Fmarkers to indicate the presence of
OL,21,Fburials.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
