PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,FThe excavation of the former St Mary's
OL,7,Fmother and baby home in Tuam is
OL,8,Fattempting to identify the remains of
OL,9,Finfants who died at the home between
OL,10,F1925 and 1961.
OL,12,FIn 2014, research led by local
OL,13,Fhistorian Catherine Corless indicated
OL,14,F796 babies and young children were
OL,15,Fburied in a sewage system at the Co
OL,16,FGalway institution across that time
OL,17,Fperiod.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,FThe Office of the Director of
OL,7,FAuthorised Intervention Tuam (ODAIT),
OL,8,Fwhich is conducting the search, said
OL,9,Fthat coffined infants were recovered
OL,10,Fand hand-excavation is continuing.
OL,12,FThe Identification Programme team
OL,13,Fcollected an additional seven DNA
OL,14,Freference samples during this period,
OL,15,Fbringing the total number taken to 62.
OL,17,FIn 2017 a commission found
OL,18,F"significant quantities" of child and
OL,19,Finfant remains in subsurface chambered
OL,20,Ftanks located in the memorial garden
OL,21,Farea of the site.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
