FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,F"To date we have started outside of
OL,7,Fthe memorial garden, in an area where
OL,8,Fthere is a map from a Galway County
OL,9,FCouncil planning file from the 1970s
OL,10,Fthat shows a burial ground, but
OL,11,Fthere's nothing on the surface to
OL,12,Findicate that there's any burials
OL,13,Fthere and then when we've excavated
OL,14,Fthere, this is where we found 99 sets
OL,15,Fof remains, really very closely
OL,16,Ftogether," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,F"So this concentration of remains
OL,7,Fburied very closely together, is
OL,8,Fextremely challenging because each
OL,9,Fburial is an archaeological context of
OL,10,Fits own and has to be recovered in
OL,11,Fthat way.
OL,13,F"Then at the other end of the site
OL,14,Fwe've dealt with and resolved a very
OL,15,Flarge area where we found no remains
OL,16,Fwhatsoever.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,F"So there's all these different
OL,7,Felements that are difficult, but I
OL,8,Fthink a year in, I'm quite happy that
OL,9,Fwe've now recovered 99 sets of remains
OL,10,Fin a place where we didn't really know
OL,11,Fthere were any remains there, so it
OL,12,Fhas, I think, justified our decision
OL,13,Fnot to start with the memorial garden,
OL,14,Fbut to leave it until later."
OL,16,FDr Niamh McCullagh, senior forensic
OL,17,Fconsultant at ODAIT, said there are a
OL,18,Fnumber of factors that make the search
OL,19,F"particularly challenging".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@]O]{D@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,F"If I work from the outside in, the
OL,7,Fchallenge of the physical location of
OL,8,Fthe site, it's within a housing estate
OL,9,Fthat is populated with people living
OL,10,Fthere, the rears of their gardens all
OL,11,Fface onto this playground area," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"The physical situation of the chamber
OL,15,Ftank where the remains were discovered
OL,16,Fin that sample excavation, they're
OL,17,Fover three metres beneath the surface,
OL,18,Fthey're in 20 individual chambers, all
OL,19,Fadjacent to one another, and that in
OL,20,Fitself is also a very physically
OL,21,Fchallenging situation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784751304
OL,3,CFurther infant remains recovered at
OL,4,CTuam former mother and baby home
OL,6,F"So, from an archaeological
OL,7,Fperspective, it is not like going out
OL,8,Fand excavating a greenfield site or an
OL,9,Fopen area where we would have a lot
OL,10,Fmore space, we have to try and manage
OL,11,Fthe space that we have to get the
OL,12,Faccess that we need to to recover the
OL,13,Fremains."
OL,15,FSt Mary's home for unmarried mothers
OL,16,Fand their children was run by the Bon
OL,17,FSecours Sisters, a religious order of
OL,18,FCatholic nuns.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
